#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-FDSReader.md:1
msgid "New `vtkFDSReader` for Fire Dynamics Simulator output"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-FDSReader.md:3
msgid ""
"You can now read in output from the Fire Dynamics Simulator (FDS, https://"
"pages.nist.gov/fds-smv/) into VTK. The reader is based on reading the `*."
"smv` meta-data file to orchestrate the reading of all the other files. It "
"supports:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-FDSReader.md:5
msgid "Grids: reading in the extents of the entire simulation domains"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-FDSReader.md:6
msgid ""
"Devices: reading in data from so called \"devices\" and representing it as "
"point data"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-FDSReader.md:7
msgid "HRR: reading in globally integrated data as a table"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-FDSReader.md:8
msgid "Slices: subsets of the entire grids with point data on them"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-FDSReader.md:9
msgid ""
"Boundaries: subsets of the grids that represent obstacles or boundaries in "
"the simulation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-FDSReader.md:11
msgid ""
"The output of the reader is a `vtkPartitionedDataSetCollection` divided into "
"the sections above."
msgstr ""
